        "faq_item_Bbrt93": {
          "settings": {
            "answer": "<p>Add one or two scoops to 8oz of cold water or your favorite milk, almond or regular milk over ice works best. Shake or stir well and enjoy. No coffee machine, no blender, no prep, ready in under 60 seconds.</p>",
            "question": "How do I prepare it?"
